{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b21dc4d5-8f04-4d50-b326-018c98e34644","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped VSTest as the default runner.**\n\nStarting with MSTest.Sdk 4.0, the SDK defaults to **Microsoft.Testing.Platform** exclusively. The produced test binary is a self-contained executable and no longer exposes the VSTest adapter entry points that `vstest.console` uses for discovery.\n\n### Fix options\n\n1. **Switch your CI to `dotnet test`** (recommended) — it supports Microsoft.Testing.Platform natively:\n   ```\n   dotnet test MyTests.csproj\n   ```\n\n2. **Re-enable the VSTest bridge** if you must keep `vstest.console`:\n   ```xml\n   <!-- In your .csproj or Directory.Build.props -->\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <UseVSTest>true</UseVSTest>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\nOption 1 is the intended forward path; option 2 is a compatibility shim.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"e857dac1-bec7-4b4a-87ad-33bc7c1be6db","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a breaking change when upgrading from MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0 to MSTest.Sdk/4.1.0, specifically regarding test discovery with vstest.console. This is a knowledge question about MSTest SDK changes, not a code task. Let me answer based on what I know about this change.\n\nIn MSTest.Sdk 4.0+, the default test runner changed. MSTest.Sdk 3.x defaulted to VSTest as the runner, but starting with MSTest.Sdk 4.0, the default runner is Microsoft.Testing.Platform (the new testing platform). When using Microsoft.Testing.Platform as the runner, the test assemblies are no longer compatible with vstest.console for discovery/execution.\n\n\nThe breaking change is that MSTest.Sdk 4.0+ now defaults to Microsoft.Testing.Platform instead of VSTest, which means vstest.console won't discover tests anymore. To resolve this, the user can either switch their CI pipeline to use `dotnet test` instead, or add a project property to revert back to the VSTest runner.","outputTokens":544,"requestId":"BD09:AF4AE:20B37D2:24EC68B:6A07D691"},"id":"ae0f16dd-d1bd-479b-b1f7-4780dbf83243","timestamp":"2026-05-16T02:29:50.926Z","parentId":"21e2fbf9-7900-47fa-a749-7da9dc46e4ba"}
